{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":null,"text":"荒山迷路，错过了宿头，不知是否能在这里借宿一宵？","tone":"疑问","chapter":36,"line_start":41,"line_end":43},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"能，当然能，莫说只借宿一宵，就算在这里住一年，也没问题。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":36,"line_start":45,"line_end":47},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":null,"text":"真的没问题？","tone":"疑问","chapter":36,"line_start":49,"line_end":49},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"一点问题也没有，不管你是不是错过了宿头，你随时来，我们随时欢迎。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":36,"line_start":51,"line_end":53},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":null,"text":"阁下虽如此，只怕别人……","tone":"犹豫","chapter":36,"line_start":55,"line_end":55},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"别人也一样，你既然来了，就是我们的客人。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":36,"line_start":57,"line_end":57},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":null,"text":"哪种客人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":36,"line_start":59,"line_end":59},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"我们的客人只有一种。","tone":"陈述","chapter":36,"line_start":61,"line_end":61},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":null,"text":"主人却有很多种。","tone":"陈述","chapter":36,"line_start":63,"line_end":63},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"哦？","tone":"疑问","chapter":36,"line_start":65,"line_end":65},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":null,"text":"有种主人随时都会逐客的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":36,"line_start":67,"line_end":67},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"那种主人这地方绝没有，你只要进了这道门，除非你自己愿意出去，否则就绝不会有任何人要你走的。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":36,"line_start":69,"line_end":71},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":null,"text":"看来我果然没有敲错门。","tone":"无奈","chapter":36,"line_start":73,"line_end":73},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":null,"text":"你的朋友都住在里面？","tone":"疑问","chapter":36,"line_start":89,"line_end":89},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"我住的是最后一间，离吃饭的地方最近。","tone":"陈述","chapter":36,"line_start":91,"line_end":91},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":null,"text":"有件事阁下虽然未说，想必也早就知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":36,"line_start":95,"line_end":97},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"哪件事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":36,"line_start":99,"line_end":99}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_guo_da_lu","name":"郭大路","alias":[],"identity":"江湖游侠","faction":"无","role":"陪伴","archetype":"战士","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"郭大路。","personality":{"traits":["义气","热血","直爽","勇敢","豪迈"],"speech_style":"直接","temperament":"热情"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":36,"line_start":20,"line_end":20,"text":"郭大路他们的原则是什么呢？"},{"chapter":36,"line_start":38,"line_end":38,"text":"第一个听到敲门声的，也许是燕七，也许是王动，但第一个抢着去应门的，却一定是郭大路。"},{"chapter":36,"line_start":45,"line_end":45,"text":"郭大路笑了，道：\"能，当然能，莫说只借宿一宵，就算在这里住一年，也没问题。"},{"chapter":36,"line_start":51,"line_end":51,"text":"郭大路道：\"一点问题也没有，不管你是不是错过了宿头，你随时来，我们随时欢迎。"},{"chapter":36,"line_start":57,"line_end":57,"text":"郭大路抢着道：\"别人也一样，你既然来了，就是我们的客人。\""},{"chapter":36,"line_start":61,"line_end":61,"text":"郭大路道：\"我们的客人只有一种。\""},{"chapter":36,"line_start":65,"line_end":65,"text":"郭大路道：\"哦？\""},{"chapter":36,"line_start":69,"line_end":69,"text":"郭大路笑道：\"那种主人这地方绝没有，你只要进了这道门，除非你自己愿意出去，否则就绝不会有任何人要你走"},{"chapter":36,"line_start":91,"line_end":91,"text":"郭大路点点头，笑道：\"我住的是最后一间，离吃饭的地方最近。\""},{"chapter":36,"line_start":99,"line_end":99,"text":"郭大路道：\"哪件事？\""}]},{"id":"char_hei_yi_ren","name":"黑衣人","alias":[],"identity":"江湖游侠","faction":"无","role":"陪伴","archetype":"战士","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"黑衣人。","personality":{"traits":["义气","热血","直爽","勇敢","豪迈"],"speech_style":"直接","temperament":"热情"},"relationships":[],"kno